{"tid":99012,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"陳雲：青年不宜從政","createTime":"2017-01-29T00:10:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-15T14:29:11.000Z","uid":389,"like":3,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"86f06773e067eb1b52838c8621564f69d08abd85","tid":99012,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T00:10:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/29/080944_2c869770d1168c506532ff6676292305.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F29%2F080944_2c869770d1168c506532ff6676292305.jpg&h=8d46e9ec&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cc0aa5c55c4eee4b20681d530aca35a15cc5ce9d","tid":99012,"uid":31748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T00:29:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">勇武如我</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n就係做佢口中「支那會」德國分部嘅卒仔"},{"pid":"7826fb9513bd3c5d3e823b55556e497d42e96094","tid":99012,"uid":29862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T02:07:58.000Z","msg":"比你選又選唔撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁撚多嘢講"},{"pid":"fd57c33373528c17eb0543bf1e4f35d56055a587","tid":99012,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T02:13:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>比你選又選唔撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁撚多嘢講</blockquote><br />\n唔好咁啦<br />\n認錯游B係佢女學生<br />\n連舊老藕都比謝撚滿要左<br />\n陳總統唯有發下嗡瘋"},{"pid":"d87df93b1367de031d19802327872682b93a12b6","tid":99012,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T02:25:12.000Z","msg":"依家黃台仰有叫人崇拜佢咩<br />\n佢自己係節目都話，9up到下年開審佢就會收皮<br />\n<br />\n依家歡迎任何有志有能之士加入本民前接捧wor 佢地會幫你手 你想選區議會乜柒佢都會動員幫你<br />\n<br />\n但陳雲有樣野岩，佢做野真係好深思熟慮，所以拉人都拉唔到佢，dq都dq唔到佢<br />\n，年宵唔會搞佢，政府冇人得閒打壓佢。"},{"pid":"94498ff115870ef217a92ecc067aabb6f9bf2ed4","tid":99012,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T02:28:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>依家黃台仰有叫人崇拜佢咩<br />\n佢自己係節目都話，9up到下年開審佢就會收皮<br />\n<br />\n依家歡迎任何有志有能之士加入本民前接捧wor 佢地會幫你手 你想選區議會乜柒佢都會動員幫你<br />\n<br />\n但陳雲有樣野岩，佢做野真係好深思熟慮，所以拉人都拉唔到佢，dq都dq唔到佢<br />\n，年宵唔會搞佢，政府冇人得閒打壓佢。</blockquote><br />\n因為無人理佢"},{"pid":"baf62cee12d50d6f278788f8605419f91b6cc622","tid":99012,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T02:28:34.000Z","msg":"另外，泛民老人利用青年新政殺死港獨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n袋巾反dq遊行都仲引用成報話青年新政係鬼（同陳雲同聲同氣），唔比佢地帶頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過講到攻擊青年新政呢<br />\n<br />\n我覺得青政其中一樣神跡就係<br />\n<br />\n令人有生之年見到港共加老泛民加熱普城聯手<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19d5d83b545751f311cd629e107b339d3f13258a","tid":99012,"uid":3685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T02:29:30.000Z","msg":"瞓左冇睇 陳雲宣左誓未"},{"pid":"a483514d054d5281d371a1b0aba77a7444c1f6b4","tid":99012,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T02:30:25.000Z","msg":"其實係咪陳雲現實冇人理，先要係網上無限樹敵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"decaa1b9468906a3a1afe921c14e9d34a4f0b5a4","tid":99012,"uid":28279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T02:30:28.000Z","msg":"老人政治？"},{"pid":"ac1e744932fca1a2165da35f01cdcb50ca032614","tid":99012,"uid":33481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T02:31:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實係咪陳雲現實冇人理，先要係網上無限樹敵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實網上都無乜人理"},{"pid":"1a81e715a27281768b46ca1f1d7ac51c8069193f","tid":99012,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T02:34:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>另外，泛民老人利用青年新政殺死港獨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n袋巾反dq遊行都仲引用成報話青年新政係鬼（同陳雲同聲同氣），唔比佢地帶頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過講到攻擊青年新政呢<br />\n<br />\n我覺得青政其中一樣神跡就係<br />\n<br />\n令人有生之年見到港共加老泛民加熱普城聯手<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n團結大和解 青政董卓連？"},{"pid":"afef139a6414528c0c24ac03b3a600e1b212d518","tid":99012,"uid":33890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T02:35:48.000Z","msg":"你班廢老做到野,洗鬼班後生從政,顛倒是非,你唔可以將命運交比後生<br />\n唔通後生就可以將命運交比你?2047你條老野都死撚左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b3e9fc43bd9023b406aeee07ee85d8de8d4a423","tid":99012,"uid":76710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T02:40:36.000Z","msg":"絕大多數青年人無咩社會經驗 好易犯錯 而導致滅黨<br />\n所以都係搵啲保守嘅中年/老年人做好過"},{"pid":"8d444053965cddff7891d5a824e180c7289ef2c3","tid":99012,"uid":9230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T02:42:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>依家黃台仰有叫人崇拜佢咩<br />\n佢自己係節目都話，9up到下年開審佢就會收皮<br />\n<br />\n依家歡迎任何有志有能之士加入本民前接捧wor 佢地會幫你手 你想選區議會乜柒佢都會動員幫你<br />\n<br />\n但陳雲有樣野岩，佢做野真係好深思熟慮，所以拉人都拉唔到佢，dq都dq唔到佢<br />\n，年宵唔會搞佢，政府冇人得閒打壓佢。</blockquote><br />\n因為無人理佢</blockquote><br />\n呢啲叫廢撚事理你"},{"pid":"37ef3a57039ee12e49d048e21ac76aa710e69510","tid":99012,"uid":53687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T02:43:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">勇武如我</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n就係做佢口中「支那會」德國分部嘅卒仔</blockquote><br />\n人唔笑，狗都吠"},{"pid":"0ed5a8c31d8fa3ffdb2abef840b8bdcccc341ee4","tid":99012,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T02:46:21.000Z","msg":"寂滅未呀屌你老母"},{"pid":"7fd26b64b21232b186cc16bfd49f9d76558c7afb","tid":99012,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T02:58:45.000Z","msg":"毓民屌泛民就老人政治<br />\n<br />\n陳雲屌青政就後生衝動<br />\n<br />\n龍門任你擺，飄移景界<br />